            <title>华为 Mate 70 系列预约破 132 万，门市大排长龙</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/mate-70/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mate-70</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/mate-70/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 19 Nov 2024 13:15:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mate 70]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mate 70 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为 Mate 70]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275979</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">华为于 11 月 18 日中午 12 时 08 分开启 Mate 70 系列的预约，短短一小时内，预约量即突破百万。华为商城显示，截至当日下午 3 时 10 分，Mate 70 系列的预约量已达 132 万，门市外大排长龙。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275980 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-4-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-4-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275986 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-5-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-5-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1275987 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-6-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-6-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241119at-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲门市出现潮华为 Mate 70 系列排队热潮（图片来源：<a href="https://www.stcn.com/article/detail/1416654.html">网易</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">华为 Mate 70 系列的预约数据惊人，门市亦出现排队热潮，多个城市的门店外排起长龙。内部消息指出，Mate 70 Pro 可能成为本次发售中最难抢购的型号，有店员透露，Pro 款年前的货源相对紧缺，而标准版和 Pro+ 款的供应情况较好。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">三款机型 Mate 70、Mate 70 Pro 和 Mate 70 Pro+ 有多种配色选择，标准版 Mate 70 有曜石黑、雪域白、云杉绿与风信紫四种颜色，而高阶版本 Mate 70 Pro+ 则新增墨韵黑、羽衣白、金丝银锦及飞天青等配色。内部配置方面，Mate 70 系列支援多种存储选项，Mate 70 和 Mate 70 Pro 最高可达 12GB RAM + 1TB，Mate 70 Pro+ 则更进一步，配备高达 16GB RAM + 1TB 的顶级配置。华为 Mate 70 系列 11 月 26 日正式推出。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料及图片来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1014/1014548.htm">快科技</a>、<a href="https://www.stcn.com/article/detail/1416654.html">网易</a>、<a href="https://www.stcn.com/article/detail/1416654.html">STCN</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/19/mate-70/mobile-phone/">华为 Mate 70 系列预约破 132 万，门市大排长龙</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
